&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an Advanced Clinical Practitioner to join our well established team of Advanced Practitioners in General Surgery and Urology at Lincoln County Hospital. We are a team of 7 ACP&#39;s and trainee ACP&#39;s who primarily manage a Surgical Ambulatory Unit which feeds directly into the acute/emergency General Surgical Services. This is an exciting opportunity for anyone who has a passion for Surgery within secondary care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If a Band 8a cannot be appointed then a Band 7 will be considered as a Trainee ACP.&lt;/p&gt;
